{"tid":1618925,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港股跌幅擴大至４４３點，特首將就禁蒙面法三點見記者","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:01:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0dc48cd75749b60c5cb6f6e52767cd47b1feae","tid":1618925,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社４日專訊》有指港府將利用《緊急法》通過訂立反蒙面法，新法將自午夜開<br />\n始生效。而政府剛宣布，行政長官林鄭月娥今日下午三時將與一眾司局長於政府總部會見傳媒。<br />\n消息令港股再進一步跌幅擴大，盤中低見２５６１２點，跌４９７點。地產股及濠賭股成沽壓對<br />\n象，新地（０００１６）跌４％為目前最差藍籌。現時，恆生指數報２５６６７點，跌４４３點<br />\n或跌１﹒７０％，主板成交４５２﹒９３億元。國企指數報１００８２點，跌１３８點或跌<br />\n１﹒３６％。<br />\n<br />\n  重磅股方面，匯豐控股（００００５）跌１﹒２７％，報５８﹒１元；港交所（００３８８<br />\n）跌２﹒１８％，報２２４﹒４元；騰訊控股（００７００）跌１﹒３５％，報３２０﹒８元；<br />\n中國移動（００９４１）跌１﹒５２％，報６４﹒７５元；友邦保險（０１２９９）跌<br />\n１﹒９４％，報７３﹒１５元。"},{"pid":"0916855017b605ec49eab1659ffc6234c09521ab","tid":1618925,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭先係真焦土派</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae719575968dfb24c41dbd2ccdb747bf11ce2cb7","tid":1618925,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"淡友們多謝林鄭"},{"pid":"71758be594febe888a5f139e6e216f95e8cc4123","tid":1618925,"uid":304470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:01:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n=============<br />\n借位擺<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/10/otPrsN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F10%2FotPrsN.png&h=f31113f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>FreeHKLive反送中綜合直播網</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://freehk.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffreehk.live%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3pFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=97e93dc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://freehk.live/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n大家有興趣可以入去睇直播<img src=\"/as